{"tid":34756,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone回美國生產？富士康：正在洽談設廠","createTime":"2016-12-11T16:07:53.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-12T00:24:06.000Z","uid":62257,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c7df80024a425f6af36b695b243241936952a6ac","tid":34756,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T16:07:53.000Z","msg":"唔通燒山真係燈到trump成為最偉大美國總統？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1913966\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1913966&d=0O233upXlWXGQUOtfKSFDQv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=9b014bb1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1913966&h=bd7cde8e\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1913966</a><br />\n<br />\n2016-12-11 13:30&nbsp;<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕川普當選美國總統後，放話要美國企業回母國設廠，並點名蘋果手機等廠商。而蘋果在中國的代工廠富士康證實，現在已經在評量在美建設工廠的可能性，也和美國相關官員展開協商，尋求雙贏的局面。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n據《星島日報》報導，富士康身為蘋果最大的代工廠，已承認赴美生產的可能性，不過另一家代工廠和碩已經否決此事，因為遷廠回美會導致製造成本增加，讓企業面臨了經營的風險。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n從另一方面來看，富士康和蘋果在美國建造工廠，可以與蘋果公司本身傑出的研發能力相輔相成，強化工廠本身的生產模式。而富士康因應美國昂貴的人力資源，有可能會採取機器人組裝的方式，避免在人力成本花費太多。"},{"pid":"4d20fe1cf3128744cd032294182bba8c3d599482","tid":34756,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T16:10:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67b36bfa934069bc7c4eef1967489ac88475ba18","tid":34756,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T16:11:16.000Z","msg":"返美國生產加價都買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9410e8db48c8c29d43f82f85e3dfcf070ce9328c","tid":34756,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,